      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must be under version control with documented release notes and regression test suite covering relevant flow regimes.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1 is deployed under ISO 9001-certified QMS. Release notes, regression test logs, and change-control records were reviewed and found compliant. Achieved level exceeds the MRL 3 required level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
